---
---
<section class="tw-section tw-section-cream" id="services">
  <div class="tw-container-wide">
    <div class="tw-section-head">
      <div class="tw-eyebrow">Association Management</div>
      <h2 class="tw-section-title">Built for the way <em>your</em> board works.</h2>
      <p class="tw-section-lede">Different communities have different mechanics, governing docs, and risk profiles. Our practice is structured around the two biggest.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="tw-pillar-grid">
      <a href="/hoa-management/" class="tw-pillar-card">
        <div class="tw-pillar-img">
          <img src="/assets/hero-aerial.jpg" alt="HOA managed by Tidewater" />
          <div class="tw-pillar-img-overlay"></div>
          <div class="tw-pillar-tag">HOA</div>
        </div>
        <div class="tw-pillar-body">
          <h3 class="tw-pillar-title">HOA Management</h3>
          <p class="tw-pillar-sub">Townhome associations, master-planned communities, and single-family HOAs across the Mid-Atlantic. Three service tiers — Full, Flex, and Financial Only.</p>
          <ul class="tw-pillar-list">
            <li>Annual management plans &amp; QA review</li>
            <li>Vendor compliance &amp; COI tracking</li>
            <li>Real-manager after-hours emergency line</li>
            <li>Board portal with real-time financial visibility</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="tw-pillar-cta">
            Explore HOA management
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="13 6 19 12 13 18"/></svg>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a href="/condo-association-management/" class="tw-pillar-card">
        <div class="tw-pillar-img">
          <img src="/assets/highrise.jpg" alt="Condo high-rise managed by Tidewater" />
          <div class="tw-pillar-img-overlay"></div>
          <div class="tw-pillar-tag">Condo</div>
        </div>
        <div class="tw-pillar-body">
          <h3 class="tw-pillar-title">Condo Association Management</h3>
          <p class="tw-pillar-sub">High-rise, mid-rise, and garden-style condominiums. Specialized in shared mechanical systems, complex reserves, and 24/7 resident expectations.</p>
          <ul class="tw-pillar-list">
            <li>Reserve studies translated into action plans</li>
            <li>Elevator, fire, HVAC management plans</li>
            <li>Special-assessment communication frameworks</li>
            <li>Building-system vendor pre-qualification</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="tw-pillar-cta">
            Explore condo management
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="13 6 19 12 13 18"/></svg>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="tw-pillar-meta">
      <div class="tw-pillar-meta-item"><span class="tw-pillar-meta-num">300+</span> communities under management</div>
      <div class="tw-pillar-meta-divider"></div>
      <div class="tw-pillar-meta-item"><span class="tw-pillar-meta-num">6 states</span> across the Mid-Atlantic</div>
      <div class="tw-pillar-meta-divider"></div>
      <div class="tw-pillar-meta-item"><span class="tw-pillar-meta-num">AAMC®</span> accredited management company</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
